-- M.Stanley offers Sihuan Pharma shares worth up to $147 mln - IFR
-- By Fiona Lau of IFR
-- Wed Apr 02, 2014 06:46AM EDT
-- None



HONG KONG, April 2 (Reuters) - Morgan Stanley Private Equity Asia launched a sale of shares in Sihuan Pharmaceutical Holdings Group Ltd. worth up to $147 million on Wednesday, IFR reported, citing a term sheet for the transaction.

The firm is offering 120 million Sihuan Pharmaceutical shares <0460.HK> at an indicative range of HK9.36 to HK$9.50 each, added IFR, a Thomson Reuters publication. The range is equivalent to a discount of up to 4.2 percent to Wednesday's closing price of HK$9.77.